Airways and Air Mauritius have signed an MOU to extend their collaboration and offer their customers more possibilities for connections.
 The two airlines have a longstanding code-share agreement. 
 ALSO READ:

KQ to send striking staff home again

 Commenting on the partnership, KQ Group Managing Director Sebastian Mikosz said the networks of the two airlines are complementary and that he was confident that the agreement would provide synergies for both firms to grow.





